{"tid":11401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高登仔另起爐灶 林早洩 : 我屹立不倒","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:56:53.000Z","uid":23601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42fec173dd51f48d573772a20c0c5a37010eae91","tid":11401,"uid":23601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"高登近日封殺高登第三方手機App「HKG+」，致群情洶湧，更令不少高登用戶過檔新成立「LIHKG討論區」。LIHKG上周五蘋果App Store上架後，旋即成為下載榜首；今日LIHKG亦已喺Android Play Store上架，LIHKG官方表示，網頁版也會稍後推出。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁林祖舜，就事件接受本報訪問，他表示高登流量未見受影響，每日Page view維持約600萬。對於有人於「LIHKG討論區」指他將被拉下台，連CEO都冇得做，他表示，「我依家就係話畀大家聽，我仍然有做！（屹立不倒？）暫時都屹立不倒！」<br />\n<br />\n他向本報指出，當年予「HKG+」作為第三方手機App，已訂立條款，包括「HKG+」不得暫存網頁內容，以及不可自行賣廣告。不過「HKG+」早於超過半年前已被發現違反承諾，其後高登已向其作警告。至一個月前，「HKG+」再被發現私自暫存網頁內容，「你都知我哋成日收律師信，變咗有啲人以為佢係我哋，封信就畀咗我哋。因為佢哋暫存我哋啲內容，我哋鏟咗就喺佢度出現返。」因此決定停止與「HKG+」合作。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，當時「HKG+」表示希望予一個月時間寬限，以向付費VIP用戶負責，「完全冇估到，原來呢個時間係籌備呢樣嘢（LIHKG）。」<br />\n<br />\n垃圾joe <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c49b08d9f04e88d362c50e4f2be797a7e7e68cc","tid":11401,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"JOE仔!!!"},{"pid":"e835f41a026f02e3c143b42968322a38ff3e60b5","tid":11401,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"林早泄 好撚黑人憎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90b8603413210432efac301df65500f292a4f41","tid":11401,"uid":14342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded1edd98b9aeeff3488fbb500b33b028c80a0f8","tid":11401,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"屹立不保就有佢份<br />\n<br />\n講撚到HKG+ save底佢d野，錯𨳊哂咁！<br />\n人地唔撚玩，送𨳊埋個code比佢，佢都唔撚要，<br />\n硬鳩係要人用佢個濕鳩官方app"},{"pid":"a97fff6695ea917f988be0c2bd8a4baa90710c57","tid":11401,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"之前個 <a href=\"http://hkg.plus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkg.plus&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b747a943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkg.plus</a> 😂😂😂"},{"pid":"f5cc6d335d1556f8af4f2d574bd71b286347cd58","tid":11401,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1e13aa4372b32c33bf3bc3444759ec3b0ea6c13","tid":11401,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫時</span></span>都屹立不倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ed7ba253e712ec0c0b5e34200ab54a5d8df2c3","tid":11401,"uid":22941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"我屹立不倒！"},{"pid":"cffa0dfb551280936e3ad242212849df2d1f5087","tid":11401,"uid":40370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"我jj都屹立不倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375274b4c6b87cac85d2d566e05119433176390f","tid":11401,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>暫時</strong>"}]}